{"tid":1687117,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［五毛運作14招］","createTime":"2019-11-01T15:10:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T15:50:14.000Z","uid":266390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9cd7e2442cdbe0762dde5b7f7ee78d2c2ae706c3","tid":1687117,"uid":266390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:10:13.000Z","msg":"呢排滲透十分嚴重<br />\n醒大家五毛維穩14招<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CMeUGeE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCMeUGeE.png&h=5dade1fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MFjESmp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMFjESmp.png&h=f52d8ef6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好敵擁我反<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記住乖乖聽話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>好似黃大仙嗰日咁嘅畫面</strong></span><br />\n唔好再有第二次啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n呢排有啲五毛會利用我哋認可嘅理念去轉移視線 擺龍門 偷換概念 仲有最陰毒嘅散播失敗主義，以及暗中分化<br />\n即係咁，分化唔一定要有屌嘅成份<br />\n佢哋而家係要分化理念上嘅嘢<br />\n舉例嚟講<br />\n<br />\n1.唔好XX，推番XX<br />\n行動post固然要推 但因為要推行動post而唔關注B就有問題<br />\n以要推A為由要令B沉底<br />\n好奇怪嘅邏輯<br />\n其實係可以叫人 <span style=\"color: red;\">關注同時 記得推行動post呀</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.分散焦點論：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">&quot;唔好查案 因為會分散焦點&rdquo;</span></span>**<br />\n<br />\n公眾焦點係有限 但絕對唔會容得下一容不下二<br />\n如果有限焦點係一個慣性 我哋要打破呢個限制 <br />\n而唔係活係限制入面<br />\n況且就算用心理學角度 人都唔係得一兩個注意力<br />\n<br />\n將A同B直接連結 好危險<br />\n唔好縱容自己適應呢啲垃圾logic<br />\n覺得查案重要嘅 有能力嘅 繼續兄弟爬山<br />\n越多對眼望住件事 真相先越可能浮面 甚至成為核彈<br />\n所有<span style=\"color: red;\">以沉底/降低關注</span>為結果嘅呼籲<br />\n都係維穩<br />\n明鑑之<br />\n<br />\n**利申只係例子<br />\n**正確唔偷換概念應該係：<br />\n唔好全世界走曬去查案 仲有其他嘢一樣咁重要<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">我哋要一齊推</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n112見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3566b606f0fb488cc812d28a1e45361e19098f6d","tid":1687117,"uid":45926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:15:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7273a598de922c6b437f51c8ddd775a0f7f40a5a","tid":1687117,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:20:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0a0497ab1eb4bb622c9effa38b8da489ca5fba9e","tid":1687117,"uid":266390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:44:12.000Z","msg":"tui 0/10"},{"pid":"01b0123d40b911e0aa19680e4fc7f4f233d8bdbc","tid":1687117,"uid":266390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:44:28.000Z","msg":"112"},{"pid":"dda7db0409c0017418672c8a4eb6867f74be914a","tid":1687117,"uid":266390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:44:39.000Z","msg":"記住去112"},{"pid":"0b0e017ada029cd265f4476555e0521113eb3e86","tid":1687117,"uid":266390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:45:23.000Z","msg":"五毛死全家"},{"pid":"595af58d8116436898ef31dc7c92d3e4add59665","tid":1687117,"uid":266390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:50:14.000Z","msg":"推唔撚郁屌"}]}